LINK: https://leetcode.com/problems/find-products-with-valid-serial-numbers/description/?envType=problem-list-v2&envId=vqwaxh5c

==> My approach:
SELECT *
FROM products
WHERE description LIKE '%SN[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]%'
     AND PATINDEX('%[^A-Za-z0-9]SN[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]%',
               ' ' + description COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN2) > 0
     AND description NOT LIKE '%[A-Za-z][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]%'
     AND description NOT LIKE '%[A-Za-z]SN[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]%'
ORDER BY product_id ; 
